text:
Julie Duval (born 31 December 1987) is a French rugby union player. She played for the France women's national rugby union team from 2012 to 2018. She participated at the 2013 Women's Six Nations Championship, 2014 Women's Rugby World Cup, 2017 Women's Rugby World Cup, 2018 Women's Six Nations Championship, and 2019 Women's Six Nations Championship.
She played with the Caen rugby team.
